org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.csv.metadata

Class CSVMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.metadata.MetaData
      • org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.csv.metadata.CSVMetaData

  • public class CSVMetaData
extends MetaData
    Class used for meta data read from CSV. Adds a method for accessing the meta data via a type string instead of calling the specific method.
